Definition: a practice in which employers give high-interest loans to workers whose entire families then labor at low wages to pay off the debt
Example: the practice is illegal in the United States
Synonyms: bondage, a, practice, in, which, employers, give, high-interest, loans, to, workers, whose, entire, families, then, labor, at, low, wages, pay, off, the, debt, is, illegal, United, States
Category: noun.state
